{"id": "ChIJV_Dbg6W5woARXyPHVDdqz3A", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 17, "displayName": {"text": "Sandeomi Hamjipark 산더미 함지박", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJV_Dbg6W5woARXyPHVDdqz3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVGNEZFJPVzF2YzNWamNtZDRNbkpXVkRobFJYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Found a giant moth in my salad half way through the bowl. I immediately asked to speK with manager. Before the manager came over, employee took my plate to show the manager. I was close enough to see and hear the interaction. The manager appeared to gesture wither her hand a d said something to the effort  of \"It probably flew in while it was flying around.\"\nWhat shocked me was not just finding an insect in my food, but how casually the situation seemed to be treated. No one appeared concerned about the fact that I had eaten a significant portion of the salad before discovering the moth.\nI had to ask for the manager a second time before she finly came to my table. When she di, the response was simply \" I'm sorry\" there was no sense of urgency,  no meaningful explanation, and no effort to reassure me that the issue would be taken seriously.\nInsects can occasionally m\nmakeend up in restaurants, but the management's response to a food safety concern says everything about how a business is operates. Based on what I personally witnessed, the handling of this situation was dismissive, unprofessional,  and completely unacceptable.\nThis was one of the worst customer service experience I have had at a restaurant. I will not be returning and cannot recommend this place to others.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Found a giant moth in my salad half way through the bowl. I immediately asked to speK with manager. Before the manager came over, employee took my plate to show the manager. I was close enough to see and hear the interaction. The manager appeared to gesture wither her hand a d said something to the effort  of \"It probably flew in while it was flying around.\"\nWhat shocked me was not just finding an insect in my food, but how casually the situation seemed to be treated. No one appeared concerned about the fact that I had eaten a significant portion of the salad before discovering the moth.\nI had to ask for the manager a second time before she finly came to my table. When she di, the response was simply \" I'm sorry\" there was no sense of urgency,  no meaningful explanation, and no effort to reassure me that the issue would be taken seriously.\nInsects can occasionally m\nmakeend up in restaurants, but the management's response to a food safety concern says everything about how a business is operates. Based on what I personally witnessed, the handling of this situation was dismissive, unprofessional,  and completely unacceptable.\nThis was one of the worst customer service experience I have had at a restaurant. I will not be returning and cannot recommend this place to others.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jason Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107670655744132100667/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYAyIrbxp4BiaVFAX-OmEEzDiCwKEidJm0q1J6boTQIkL0zA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T15:33:15.193133948Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVGNEZFJPVzF2YzNWamNtZDRNbkpXVkRobFJYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVGNEZFJPVzF2YzNWamNtZDRNbkpXVkRobFJYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9a583dbf057:0x70cf6a3754c7235f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_Dbg6W5woARXyPHVDdqz3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwcmNHcDBVbk5NVjJrNUxXcFdZMEpxVERCTlIwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "OMG, WHAT A DELICIOUS RESTAURANT!! I have been looking for fire roasted PORK RIBS for years and these are the best in LA without a doubt. Legendary Lasung chefs deliver the best multi-dimensional tasting PORK RIBS ever!!. Yeah they are that good. It is even better than the ones from that restaurant near Fullerton.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "OMG, WHAT A DELICIOUS RESTAURANT!! I have been looking for fire roasted PORK RIBS for years and these are the best in LA without a doubt. Legendary Lasung chefs deliver the best multi-dimensional tasting PORK RIBS ever!!. Yeah they are that good. It is even better than the ones from that restaurant near Fullerton.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "pete", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108805549117745599235/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWp4wFMd-OBsT-G00i7ZBjZXqBvjnvip0ISZ0KUH3_VEHbHQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T10:37:10.568980912Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwcmNHcDBVbk5NVjJrNUxXcFdZMEpxVERCTlIwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwcmNHcDBVbk5NVjJrNUxXcFdZMEpxVERCTlIwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9a583dbf057:0x70cf6a3754c7235f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_Dbg6W5woARXyPHVDdqz3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JMFdTMVhNMnhvTlVGWmMxZEJkVkUwU1d4cFoyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great ribs. I wolfed it down. Coming back for more. Great service", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great ribs. I wolfed it down. Coming back for more. Great service", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chin Park", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113911466380328642921/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDRhlVv7pDgFe2qPF9ak3x20V_-DuY1LHHSYlaNyiQQXSqJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-11T03:02:16.768325052Z", "f